The paper deals with location privacy-preserving mechanisms, which is a topic that falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of auxiliary metrics to guide the search for optimal mechanisms, which involves data analysis and machine learning techniques (cs.DB, cs.LG). Additionally, the paper mentions information theory (cs.IT) and the evaluation of privacy protection mechanisms (cs.SI).
